{"type": "article", "id": 28279, "title": "编织灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-16T06:40:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140236bAgtXkvBKJCha8xq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>这个名为 Loop lamps 的灯具系列由来自 <a href=\"http://www.mottoform.com/\">mottoform</a> 工作室的 Elizabeth Salonen 所设计，是一个将传统手工艺与技术结合的作品。吊灯由内部的塑料组件和手工编织的纸绳灯罩组成，均在芬兰本土进行制作。由于工匠的手法各有差异，没有两个灯会是完全一样的。它们最终的形态由针织图案、LED 灯管盒的形状以及重力的作用所决定，带给人一种多变而温暖的感觉。这个系列目前仍处于原型阶段，Salonen 正在寻找有兴趣的制作商合作生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140234eCBHu8QwijOb5yWV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.32396088\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140235zuId9DRgK2BNpJ4G.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.50488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140235GjN0MYCibKalUm2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.45843521\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021402369EOFV5Scp81hZ7jy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39608802\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}